Translation files live here. Generate the source template with:
  cd wp-content/themes/navigate-peptides
  wp i18n make-pot . languages/navigate-peptides.pot \
      --domain=navigate-peptides --skip-js

Per-locale translations (e.g. navigate-peptides-es_ES.po) compile to .mo and load
via load_theme_textdomain() registered in functions.php.
